<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf6b3bf4c-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s42103"><num value="42103">§ 42103.</num><heading> No preference to Government-owned vessels</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A regulation may not give a vessel owned by the United States Government a preference over a vessel owned by citizens of the United States and documented under the laws of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf6b3bf4d-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/304/s7">Pub. L. 109–304, § 7</ref>, <date date="2006-10-06">Oct. 6, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1549">120 Stat. 1549</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
